; Declarative wodoc config for the Ocsigen blog (served at /blog).
; The blog is built "flat" (like the vitrine, doc/vitrine) by doc/blog/build.sh,
; not by the versioned `wodoc build`; this config only declares the (blog ...)
; stanza that `wodoc blog-nav`, `wodoc blog-feed` and `assemble --blog-config`
; read. Posts are doc/blog/posts/YYYY-MM-DD-slug.mld; they deploy at
; /blog/posts/<slug>.html (relative to this config's cwd = doc/blog).
(project blog)
(title Blog)
(blog
 (dir posts)
 (out posts)
 (heading "Blog")
 (latest 5))
